Try these in 2023 for a successful year: 

1- Discuss starting a new business, investing, gym and healthy lifestyle, self development with your friends. 

2- Take a risk this year. Whether it’s in business or your personal life, take a leap of faith. 

3- Train yourself to take nothing personally. Most of the time it’s not about you, it’s about them. This will keep you sane.

4- Don’t chase money, go after the freedom that comes with having money. Two different goals. 

5 - Put that idea into action, and don’t worry about looking silly or stupid. Noah looked like a fool until it started to rain. 

6- Be uncomfortable for a few months to be comfortable living the life you want to create for yourself. 

7- Learn a new skill, a new language, do something different or you will be doing the same thing that is not bringing you happiness for the rest of your life. 

8- Not everyone is called or meant to be an entrepreneur. If the 9-5 is working well for you, awesome! Be you and do you! 

9- Don’t tell people more than they need to know. They can guess, lie, misinterpret or say whatever they think they know. 

10- Whatever wrong you’ve done before, make peace with it and let it go. You are not perfect. You are capable of making mistakes. Stop hiding from the shadows of the past. Don’t be trapped in the darkness of shattered memories. Let the light shine through and shine upon you. Forgive yourself, because it’s the only way you can start again and do better. 

What resonates with you? - Happy Monday. ✨🤍
